<number id="B5350C474C7FFF88FDB1F91F6D1FF8AB" box="[608,623,1789,1815]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" value="1.0">1</number>
ɗ 
<number id="B5350C474C7FFF88FD52F91F6DE2F8AB" box="[643,658,1789,1815]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" value="1.0">1</number>
Ψ 
<collectingCountry id="7BEA5EF04C7FFF88FD7CF91F6C34F8AB" box="[685,836,1789,1815]" name="South Africa" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">South Africa</collectingCountry>
(Eastern Cape): Willowmore, 
